{"tid":1353264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"727我地一定要入元朗","createTime":"2019-07-23T02:32:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T05:01:26.000Z","uid":202464,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cb56800bc9a1f8682017cc72f191700d70a56871","tid":1353264,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:32:37.000Z","msg":"琴日一單消息又話刀手又話沒差別砍人<br />\n結果成個新界死城咁<br />\n我地要話比佢地班新界黑社會知<br />\n呢度係香港<br />\n我地係香港人<br />\n我地團結一齊，唔好講呢班新界牛屎仔<br />\n掃平全港黑社會都得<br />\n我地做緊政治運動，既然佢地選擇企向政府果邊<br />\n佢地就係我地既敵人<br />\n只要有十萬人走入元朗，我睇下邊班黑社會夠膽出黎攪我地<br />\n過去金鐘我地有40萬人，有100萬人，有200萬人<br />\n我地愈多人入去，就愈安全<br />\n我呼籲所有人著黑衫入元朗，我地唔可以放棄新界既手足，今後我地邊度既手足出事，我地就踩入果區<br />\n我地遍地開花，我地要將呢個運動向全香港發展"},{"pid":"a2da2213b36b90781452b369df673bc8e2899e28","tid":1353264,"uid":32861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:43:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">721宣言</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzfNKZRPQHZk&d=3INNoT16QYf2eZrqTwRUigHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=0500e68a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk</a><br />\n<br />\n條片只有<span style=\"color: green;\">3000views</span> <br />\n但留言勁多5毛 某程度證明有用<br />\n<br />\n大家幫手留言 引啲5毛一齊推上Youtube熱門<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">歡迎轉發及引用推Post</code></pre>"},{"pid":"6fddb1cff9be433ed14c8fed60099047ea91f214","tid":1353264,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:59:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4558dd22e0dab6b68957b51cca12af7aafb9055a","tid":1353264,"uid":164938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T03:00:50.000Z","msg":"網上仲有好多人唔知係27定28號<br />\n係改左做27號光復 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wEBdKMw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwEBdKMw.png&h=d464cba0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BoFYVTc.png\" data-thumbna